;"}, "b": [{"_value": "-verify_other"}], "i": [{"_value": "file"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:17%;"}, "small": [{"_value": "URI"}, {"_value": "OCSP"}, {"_value": "PEM, DER,"}], "_values": ["File or", "containing additional certificates to search when attempting\nto locate the", "response signing\ncertificate. Some responders omit the actual signer\u2019s\ncertificate from the response: this option can be used to\nsupply the necessary certificate in such cases. The input\ncan be in", "or PKCS#12 format."]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:11%;"}, "b": [{"_value": "-trust_other"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:17%;"}, "b": [{"_value": "-verify_other"}], "_values": ["The certificates specified by\nthe", "option should be explicitly trusted\nand no additional checks will be performed on them. This is\nuseful when the complete responder certificate chain is not\navailable or trusting a root", "is not\nappropriate."], "small": [{"_value": "CA"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:11%;"}, "b": [{"_value": "-VAfile"}], "i": [{"_value": "file"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:17%;"}, "small": [{"_value": "URI"}, {"_value": "PEM,\nDER,"}], "_values": ["File or", "containing explicitly trusted responder certificates.\nEquivalent to the", "and", "options. The input can be in", "or PKCS#12 format."], "b": [{"_value": "-verify_other"}, {"_value": "-trust_other"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:11%;"}, "b": [{"_value": "-noverify"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:17%;"}, "small": [{"_value": "OCSP"}], "_values": ["Don\u2019t attempt to verify\nthe", "response signature or the nonce\nvalues. This option will normally only be used for debugging\nsince it disables all verification of the responders\ncertificate."]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:11%;"}, "b": [{"_value": "-no_intern"}]}, {"_attributes": {"style": "margin-left:17%;"}, "small": [{"_value": "OCSP"}], "_values": ["Ignore certificates contained\ni